						href="board_list1.jsp">3</a></span> &nbsp;&nbsp; <span><a>&gt;</a></span>
					&nbsp; <span><a>&gt;&gt;</a></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!--//페이지넘버-->
		</div>
	</div>
	<!--//하단 디자인 -->

</body>
